  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, whisk together BBQ sauce, smoked paprika, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add lamb pieces to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Cover the bowl with plastic wrap and refrigerate for at least 2 hours or overnight.",
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread marinated lamb onto skewers.",
    "Brush kebabs with vegetable oil and season with additional salt and pepper if desired.",
    "Grill kebabs for 8-10 minutes per side, or until lamb reaches a safe internal temperature of 145°F.",
